Class TrafficNetwork

  • java.lang.Object
    • tn.Network
      • tn.TrafficNetwork

  • public class TrafficNetwork
extends Network
    A Network represents the directed-graph topology , i.e. nodes, directed links and allows properties to be associated with links
    Author:
    Saleh Ibrahim
